    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45355190_41_3103-3174",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "3103-3174",
      "markText": "在分工非常细致的日本半导体企业中，舛冈成为极少数拥有从研发、生产到销售的全盘经验的人才，这对他后来在闪存研发上取得革命性的突破有着极大的帮助。",
      "totalCount": 1512,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45355190&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=3103&rangeEnd=3174",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b3213072b410b624b124b?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=3103&rangeEnd=3174"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45355190_56_14955-15003",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "14955-15003",
      "markText": "摩尔定律走向终结，还有一个重要原因是光刻机的研发到极紫外技术时已到极限，光学光刻机至此已到终点。",
      "totalCount": 1411,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45355190&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=14955&rangeEnd=15003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b3213072b410b624b124b?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=14955&rangeEnd=15003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45355190_40_2376-2438",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "2376-2438",
      "markText": "美国的这一操作开了个很坏的先例，那就是以国家安全为借口，将经济层面的争端上升到政治层面，对他国的高科技产业进行赤裸裸的打压。",
      "totalCount": 1309,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45355190&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=2376&rangeEnd=2438",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b3213072b410b624b124b?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=2376&rangeEnd=2438"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45355190_41_9695-9748",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "9695-9748",
      "markText": "参观大分厂结束后，三星电子就把大分厂管辖生产线的生产部长给挖走了，然后建了一个几乎与大分厂一模一样的工厂。",
      "totalCount": 1305,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45355190&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=9695&rangeEnd=9748",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b3213072b410b624b124b?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=9695&rangeEnd=9748"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45355190_58_12243-12307",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "12243-12307",
